summary: Saved in the keep with Ralof on LV1
descriptionHtml:
Install: place in C:\\Users\\[username]\\Documents\\My Games\\Skyrim\\Saves\\

To change her appearance open console with ~ and type showracemenu

EDIT: Updated the file, just made her look a little better, and got rid of the red lipstick

Mods I used, installed in this order:
No More Blocky Faces
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=30
Detailed Faces v2
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=26
High Quality Eyes
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=498
Detailed Lips
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=689
Amazing Smooth Females Complete (I used the low smoothing one)
http://www.skyrimnexus.com/downloads/file.php?id=140
